                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Lew</placeName><add>?</add>:\n                                                  <date>20 March 1848</date></p>\n                              <p>My dear Sir,</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Enclosed you will receive a ten<lb/> dollar ($10)\n                                        Bill of the Western Bank of<lb/>\n                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>, for the Cheap Jewish\n                                        publi-<lb/>cation society_for the following persons<lb/>\n                                        <hi rend=\"underline\">towit</hi>\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Solomon Cohen</persName>,\n                                                  <persName>Octavius Cohen</persName>, <persName>A.\n                                                  Minis</persName><lb/>\n                                        <persName>Miss Fanny Y. Cohen</persName>, (<hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">care of <persName>Octavius\n                                                  Cohen</persName></hi>) <persName>Isaac<lb/>\n                                                  Cohen</persName>, <persName>M. S.\n                                        Cohen</persName>, <persName>I. Dela Ilotta</persName>,\n                                                  <persName>Miss<lb/> T. Minis</persName> (care of\n                                                  <persName>A. Minis</persName>) <persName>Miss C.\n                                                  Cohen</persName><lb/> (care of <persName>Solomon\n                                                  Cohen</persName>) &amp; <persName>Theodore\n                                                  Minis</persName><lb/> in all ten. I will try &amp;\n                                        get you a few<lb/> more—All of the above are original\n                                        sub-<lb/>scribers, except the last named, who is a<lb/> new\n                                        one. Do acknowledge the receipt of<lb/> this &amp; tell me\n                                        when the year com-<lb/>mences, so that hereafter, I may\n                                        be<lb/> more regular.</p>\n                              <p>I wrote you some time since sending<lb/> you ten Dolls: for five\n                                        Copies of <persName>Miss<lb/> Aguilar's</persName> Jewish\n                                        Faith. W<hi rend=\"underline\">as the letter<lb/>\n                                                  received?</hi> I also wrote you a few<lb/> days\n                                        since a review of <add>?</add>\n                                        <persName>O'Neal's</persName><lb/> opinion. I hope it\n                                        reached you in<lb/> safety. You will now have an<lb/>\n                                        opportunity of answering my <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                                        >three</hi></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3kh0fg03/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
